%p Dear #{h(@attendee.full_name)},

%p Your registration as #{I18n.t(@attendee.registration_type.title)} priced #{number_to_currency(@attendee.base_price, :locale => :pt)} at #{@attendee.conference.name} was confirmed successfully.

- unless @attendee.courses.empty?
  %p Besides the conference, you also registered for the following courses:
  %ul
    - @attendee.courses.each do |course|
      %li '#{I18n.t(course.full_name)}' priced #{number_to_currency(course.price(@attendee.registration_date), :locale => :pt)}

%p Please look for the event registration desk starting June 27th at 7 A.M. to get your credentials. The event will take place at Fábrica de Negócios, Av. Monsenhor Tabosa 740, Iracema beach, with entrance through Rua João Cordeiro, at Fortaleza, Ceará.

